data.description: Don't miss out on this Beautifully renovated home. it was renovated in 2019, with a new roof, new water heater, fresh coat of paint and stainless steal appliances. this home offers a spacious floor plan, open living room and a large island in the kitchen that is ideal for entertaining. Nice and quite fenced back yard with a small shed and lots lots of potential to make it your own. With a little elbow grease, and some lifting, you can easily bring this home back to life!
